A wild-eyed, chaotic spirit made of swirling flames and scattered playing cards, the incarnation of mayhem rampages through a cluttered room filled with toppled trade binders, spilled coins, and shimmering magic auras; the creature's fiery form sports a manic grin, while valuable cards like Jace swirl perilously in the air, all rendered in a bold, energetic, and stylized comic-book style reflecting the unpredictable energy and humor of the card.